1
00:01:05,080 --> 00:01:06,640
Do me a small favor first.

2
00:01:06,640 --> 00:01:07,440
What is it?

3
00:01:08,160 --> 00:01:10,560
Leak Shen Qiangwei's birth chart details.

4
00:01:11,080 --> 00:01:13,240
Miss Shen, are you planning...

5
00:01:13,560 --> 00:01:15,289
The Emperor is weak these days.

6
00:01:15,680 --> 00:01:18,200
Using a wedding to ward off his illness as an excuse

7
00:01:18,200 --> 00:01:21,320
is justification enough to openly send Shen Qiangwei into the palace.

8
00:01:21,320 --> 00:01:24,120
Miss Shen, that is a brilliant move.

9
00:01:24,840 --> 00:01:27,480
But aren't you afraid that once Miss Shen gains power,

10
00:01:27,480 --> 00:01:29,600
she and Shen Zhao will turn on you?

11
00:01:29,920 --> 00:01:31,980
They aren't even worth my attention.

12
00:01:32,039 --> 00:01:34,880
Then what about my brother, Bulei?

13
00:01:37,600 --> 00:01:40,640
I heard there's always been a prophecy on the grassland.

14
00:01:40,640 --> 00:01:44,039
That in ten years, a new queen will emerge.

15
00:01:45,039 --> 00:01:46,120
I'm curious.

16
00:01:46,520 --> 00:01:47,979
With a prophecy like that,

17
00:01:48,240 --> 00:01:49,970
knowing Bulei's personality,

18
00:01:50,560 --> 00:01:52,440
why didn't he take precautions

19
00:01:53,759 --> 00:01:55,090
and deal with you first?

20
00:01:56,160 --> 00:01:57,820
My brother and I are siblings.

21
00:01:58,240 --> 00:01:59,479
We are of one mind.

22
00:02:01,960 --> 00:02:03,280
There is only one reason

23
00:02:03,280 --> 00:02:05,560
why he wouldn't see you as a threat.

24
00:02:05,880 --> 00:02:06,610
What reason?

25
00:02:07,720 --> 00:02:11,160
Marquis Bai brought a girl back from the border eleven years ago.

26
00:02:11,160 --> 00:02:13,400
Plus, you're very interested in Manchuan.

27
00:02:13,400 --> 00:02:14,660
Looking at it this way,

28
00:02:15,480 --> 00:02:17,040
the answer is obvious.

29
00:02:18,720 --> 00:02:19,600
Miss Shen,

30
00:02:20,120 --> 00:02:22,640
you really never cease to surprise me.

31
00:02:24,560 --> 00:02:25,490
Princess Tuoya,

32
00:02:25,920 --> 00:02:29,280
you should be glad I'm not your enemy.

33
00:02:37,079 --> 00:02:37,840
Princess,

34
00:02:37,840 --> 00:02:40,320
isn't that Shen Lingbo a bit too arrogant?

35
00:02:40,800 --> 00:02:42,320
But she is smart.

36
00:02:42,440 --> 00:02:43,320
So,

37
00:02:43,440 --> 00:02:45,680
are we just going to let her walk all over us?

38
00:02:45,680 --> 00:02:46,480
Of course not.

39
00:02:47,640 --> 00:02:50,120
It's time to find some new allies.

40
00:02:55,160 --> 00:02:56,890
You made this move too hastily.

41
00:02:58,720 --> 00:03:00,280
The situation is too chaotic.

42
00:03:00,280 --> 00:03:02,340
I just wanted to cut the Gordian knot.

43
00:03:03,240 --> 00:03:05,240
But the more I cut, the messier it gets.

44
00:03:05,240 --> 00:03:06,520
It might not be faster.

45
00:03:10,000 --> 00:03:11,930
Huanghuacai, someone's outside.

46
00:03:12,040 --> 00:03:13,600
They say they're looking for the Third Prince.

47
00:03:13,600 --> 00:03:15,860
My dad is asking if you want to let them in.

48
00:03:16,040 --> 00:03:17,500
Someone is looking for me?

49
00:03:18,560 --> 00:03:19,760
It's Princess Tuoya.

50
00:03:20,040 --> 00:03:21,079
How did you guess?

51
00:03:21,280 --> 00:03:23,000
The Third Prince isn't in the palace.

52
00:03:23,000 --> 00:03:25,680
They would definitely want to confirm your whereabouts.

53
00:03:25,680 --> 00:03:28,079
Should I see her then?

54
00:03:28,440 --> 00:03:30,200
This is the Zhongyi Marquis Manor.

55
00:03:30,200 --> 00:03:32,440
No matter how bold the people from Yueshi are,

56
00:03:32,440 --> 00:03:34,570
they wouldn't dare lay a finger on you.

57
00:03:35,000 --> 00:03:36,320
Did Tuoya come alone?

58
00:03:36,760 --> 00:03:38,120
Good guess.

59
00:03:39,000 --> 00:03:41,530
Then you might as well see her, Your Highness.

60
00:03:42,400 --> 00:03:43,280
Your Highness.

61
00:03:48,320 --> 00:03:49,960
Have you been well lately?

62
00:03:51,040 --> 00:03:53,000
I have something to discuss with you.

63
00:03:53,000 --> 00:03:55,060
I wonder if we could speak in private.

64
00:03:56,280 --> 00:03:58,210
These two are pillars of the state.

65
00:03:59,320 --> 00:04:01,600
You have always been so charming

66
00:04:01,720 --> 00:04:03,240
and dignified, Your Highness.

67
00:04:03,240 --> 00:04:05,280
Why are you so cold today?

68
00:04:06,200 --> 00:04:08,640
Is there something wrong with this princess's head?

69
00:04:08,640 --> 00:04:10,480
Coming here just to say such cheesy things.

70
00:04:10,480 --> 00:04:11,610
What a waste of time.

71
00:04:12,040 --> 00:04:13,970
My husband really is the smart one.

72
00:04:15,160 --> 00:04:16,760
I won't beat around the bush.

73
00:04:17,120 --> 00:04:20,320
I came to find you today regarding the marriage alliance.

74
00:04:20,320 --> 00:04:21,399
Marriage alliance?

75
00:04:21,399 --> 00:04:23,000
Yueshi is full of sincerity.

76
00:04:23,320 --> 00:04:25,480
We wish to form an alliance with Great Sheng

77
00:04:25,480 --> 00:04:27,280
to secure the borders together.

78
00:04:27,880 --> 00:04:29,320
I know about the marriage alliance.

79
00:04:29,320 --> 00:04:30,560
I won't stand in the way.

80
00:04:30,560 --> 00:04:32,920
I'm afraid you've misunderstood my meaning, Your Highness.

81
00:04:32,920 --> 00:04:34,200
I mean to say,

82
00:04:34,680 --> 00:04:37,880
my marriage partner doesn't have to be the Emperor.

83
00:04:38,280 --> 00:04:40,720
You mean you want to marry me?

84
00:04:43,120 --> 00:04:46,520
No. I will never use a marriage alliance as a bargaining chip.

85
00:04:46,960 --> 00:04:48,159
But what if I told you,

86
00:04:48,320 --> 00:04:50,080
if you marry me,

87
00:04:50,520 --> 00:04:52,650
you won't just get a Princess Consort,

88
00:04:52,680 --> 00:04:54,680
but the entire Yueshi Kingdom?

89
00:04:55,080 --> 00:04:57,159
Yueshi Kingdom just wants to use this opportunity

90
00:04:57,159 --> 00:04:58,600
to infiltrate Dasheng.

91
00:04:59,200 --> 00:05:00,040
Princess Tuoya,

92
00:05:00,040 --> 00:05:02,000
why make it sound so noble?

93
00:05:02,600 --> 00:05:04,000
But there is no conflict.

94
00:05:04,440 --> 00:05:06,520
Dasheng needs stability at the borders,

95
00:05:06,520 --> 00:05:09,000
and I need a foothold.

96
00:05:09,080 --> 00:05:10,040
Princess Tuoya,

97
00:05:10,840 --> 00:05:12,300
I am not interested in you.

98
00:05:12,440 --> 00:05:13,520
Don't force it.

99
00:05:16,000 --> 00:05:17,600
We have a distinguished guest.

100
00:05:17,600 --> 00:05:18,800
Let me introduce you.

101
00:05:18,840 --> 00:05:20,280
This is Princess Tuoya.

102
00:05:22,920 --> 00:05:25,040
Did I come at a bad time?

103
00:05:25,200 --> 00:05:28,320
I heard you talking about a marriage alliance or something.

104
00:05:28,320 --> 00:05:29,800
Third Prince,

105
00:05:29,800 --> 00:05:32,460
you clearly said I was the only one in your heart.

106
00:05:34,080 --> 00:05:35,810
When are you coming to marry me?

107
00:05:35,920 --> 00:05:37,040
But let me tell you,

108
00:05:37,320 --> 00:05:39,650
our Bai family does not allow concubines.

109
00:05:39,720 --> 00:05:41,240
If you like some princess,

110
00:05:42,640 --> 00:05:44,570
you'll have to keep her on the side.

111
00:05:45,400 --> 00:05:46,860
I only have you in my heart.

112
00:05:49,440 --> 00:05:51,040
Since you are not interested,

113
00:05:51,040 --> 00:05:52,770
I won't disturb you any longer.

114
00:05:53,840 --> 00:05:55,720
By the way, Miss Song.

115
00:05:56,040 --> 00:05:58,480
I might have some intelligence you need.

116
00:05:58,480 --> 00:06:00,160
Can we talk alone?

117
00:06:08,320 --> 00:06:11,880
Third Prince, I just wanted to help you out of that situation.

118
00:06:12,040 --> 00:06:12,500
Please,

119
00:06:12,840 --> 00:06:14,000
do not take offense.

120
00:06:17,320 --> 00:06:18,050
Brother Bai,

121
00:06:24,440 --> 00:06:27,200
Third Prince, ask me to play chess next time.

122
00:06:27,280 --> 00:06:28,800
I'm also very good at it.

123
00:06:38,080 --> 00:06:39,800
Brother Bai, you lost.

124
00:06:47,560 --> 00:06:49,440
What do you have to say to me, Princess Tuoya?

125
00:06:49,440 --> 00:06:52,200
I've always thought Miss Song was a smart person.

126
00:06:52,480 --> 00:06:53,720
In that case,

127
00:06:53,720 --> 00:06:56,320
let's talk about things between smart people.

128
00:06:57,040 --> 00:06:58,080
What do you want to talk about?

129
00:06:58,080 --> 00:07:00,200
I know that all these years, you

130
00:07:00,200 --> 00:07:02,840
have been investigating the Song family military pay case.

131
00:07:02,840 --> 00:07:04,200
It's a pity that after investigating for so long,

132
00:07:04,200 --> 00:07:06,120
you're just going in circles around old accounts.

133
00:07:06,120 --> 00:07:09,840
If you want to know who took that 500,000 taels,

134
00:07:09,920 --> 00:07:11,320
perhaps I can help you.

135
00:07:12,880 --> 00:07:14,240
That winter month,

136
00:07:14,240 --> 00:07:17,520
the Song Army suddenly adjusted accounts during the march,

137
00:07:17,520 --> 00:07:20,120
causing the provisions to go missing en route.

138
00:07:20,600 --> 00:07:24,240
If you want to hear more,

139
00:07:24,760 --> 00:07:27,040
we should talk about our cooperation.

140
00:07:27,440 --> 00:07:29,280
You know quite a lot of details.

141
00:07:29,280 --> 00:07:32,000
Yueshi Kingdom's spies have always been good.

142
00:07:32,680 --> 00:07:34,159
I can investigate it myself.

143
00:07:34,159 --> 00:07:35,920
But in this matter,

144
00:07:36,040 --> 00:07:39,480
some people don't want the truth to surface.

145
00:07:40,040 --> 00:07:42,080
Relying on your strength alone...

146
00:07:44,080 --> 00:07:45,200
What do you want?

147
00:07:45,480 --> 00:07:47,680
I want to be friends with you.

148
00:07:48,400 --> 00:07:50,130
I don't think we can be friends.

149
00:07:50,760 --> 00:07:52,720
Every debt has its debtor.

150
00:07:53,000 --> 00:07:56,000
The person who ordered the slaughter of the Song Army was Bulei.

151
00:07:56,000 --> 00:07:57,659
You don't know me well enough.

152
00:07:58,920 --> 00:08:01,580
Thirty thousand soldiers of the Song Army died.

153
00:08:01,600 --> 00:08:02,960
A full thirty thousand.

154
00:08:03,040 --> 00:08:05,320
This is a blood feud.

155
00:08:05,320 --> 00:08:08,560
But you still want to know the answer, don't you?

156
00:08:08,600 --> 00:08:09,400
Yes.

157
00:08:09,840 --> 00:08:11,280
But not from you.

158
00:08:11,320 --> 00:08:14,080
Then take your time investigating.

159
00:08:14,160 --> 00:08:16,040
I hope when you find the truth,

160
00:08:16,040 --> 00:08:18,170
you won't be too surprised, Miss Song.

161
00:08:19,800 --> 00:08:21,800
I won't see you out, Princess Tuoya.

162
00:08:37,080 --> 00:08:39,120
What a coincidence, Third Prince.

163
00:08:45,280 --> 00:08:46,000
Miss Bai.

164
00:08:48,040 --> 00:08:49,560
Just call me Chaohua.

165
00:09:00,400 --> 00:09:02,200
The weather is quite nice today.

166
00:09:05,120 --> 00:09:05,920
The weather?

167
00:09:09,560 --> 00:09:12,160
The weather is indeed nice.

168
00:09:15,920 --> 00:09:17,600
It's my first time, after all.

169
00:09:17,640 --> 00:09:19,640
You can do this, Chaohua.

170
00:09:25,240 --> 00:09:26,640
Third Prince.

171
00:09:26,920 --> 00:09:27,720
Miss Bai.

172
00:09:27,920 --> 00:09:30,520
What a coincidence.

173
00:09:33,200 --> 00:09:34,680
Please, sit.

174
00:09:36,400 --> 00:09:37,000
Miss Bai.

175
00:09:38,480 --> 00:09:40,760
I told you,

176
00:09:41,040 --> 00:09:43,240
just call me Chaohua.

177
00:09:44,480 --> 00:09:45,040
Chaohua.

178
00:09:46,200 --> 00:09:47,760
It really is a coincidence.

179
00:09:49,000 --> 00:09:49,560
Right?

180
00:09:51,760 --> 00:09:54,720
The weather does seem nice today.

181
00:09:55,720 --> 00:09:56,680
It is indeed.

182
00:09:57,200 --> 00:09:57,860
Quite nice.

183
00:09:58,920 --> 00:09:59,360
Nice.

184
00:10:04,920 --> 00:10:06,850
Why hasn't he complimented me yet?

185
00:10:12,880 --> 00:10:14,000
What kind of tea is this?
